    dc:creator "Lisi, Oscar; Binda, Maria Grazia; Pilato, Giovanni" ;
    dc:date "2016" ;
    dc:title "Eremobiotus ginevrae sp. nov. and Paramacrobiotus pius sp. nov., two new species of Eutardigrada" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267190> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.267190>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Paramacrobiotus pius sp. nov. (holotype): A, Bucco-pharyngeal apparatus. B, Claws of the first pair of legs (arrow indicates the accessory points). C, Claws of the hind legs (arrows indicate the lunules). D, Detail of the egg; the apical short spines of the egg processes are visible (arrow). E, Detail of the egg; the reticular ornamentation of the egg processes is visible (arrows). F, Detail of the egg shell; the sculpture of the areolae is visible (arrows). Scale bar = 10 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/267190/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

